  border-radius: 0.1875rem;
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .mirror-flash {
    animation: none;
  }
}
```

`rgb(245 158 11 / 0.15)` is Tailwind's `amber-500/15` in plain CSS. We use a single tone for both light and dark themes — amber at 15% alpha reads as a soft warm wash in both, and avoiding a `.dark` selector keeps the rule simple.

